to talk more.

22:04.840 --> 22:06.840
Food's on me; keep it under
a thousand bucks.

22:06.880 --> 22:08.430
It's been a pleasure.

22:08.470 --> 22:10.720
I'll send ten percent of
my matzo balls to you, Lew.

22:10.760 --> 22:12.930
And I'll take it.

22:12.970 --> 22:14.770
He's picking up our tab.

22:14.810 --> 22:16.520
Excellent.

22:16.560 --> 22:19.020
Next time, let's meet in
the shoe department at Saks.

22:19.060 --> 22:20.860
VONNIE: I don't care what
your fucking title is.

22:20.900 --> 22:22.690
-It's house manager.
-Your dirtbag friends come in

22:22.730 --> 22:24.570
and sit in my section,
they got to order.

22:24.610 --> 22:26.860
They don't got to order, they're
guests of the house manager.

22:26.900 --> 22:28.910
Then sit them
in another section.

22:28.950 --> 22:30.990
