your section.

22:31.030 --> 22:32.410
I fucking quit, Susie.

22:32.450 --> 22:33.700
I'm heartbroken.

22:33.740 --> 22:35.700
(phone ringing)

22:35.750 --> 22:37.830
-Gaslight.
-MIDGE: Hey, it's Midge.

22:37.870 --> 22:39.960
