for you with Jackie.

22:40.000 --> 22:41.880
-Did he give them to you?
-Hang on.

22:41.920 --> 22:44.710
Jackie, did you have messages
from Midge for me?

22:44.760 --> 22:46.970
-Possibly. -Asshole.
-Asshole.

22:47.010 --> 22:50.090
You can't just throw in a random
off-topic "asshole."

22:50.140 --> 22:51.390
An asshole has to be motivated.

22:51.430 --> 22:52.810
You breathe. It's motivated.

22:52.850 --> 22:54.680
Hey, you guys have got to get
a divorce.

22:54.720 --> 22:56.100
I mean it.

22:56.140 --> 22:57.560
What was your message?

22:57.600 --> 22:59.600
I was just calling
to touch base.

22:59.650 --> 23:01.310
You left early the other night.

23:01.360 --> 23:03.650
-Well, they ran out of butter.
-MIDGE: Butter. Okay.

23:03.690 --> 23:06.690
Uh, well, we should
get together again.

23:06.740 --> 23:08.780
-Soon, okay?
-SUSIE: Yeah, sure.

23:08.820 --> 23:11.240
Hey, what was the deal
with you and that guy?

23:11.280 --> 23:14.080
-What guy? You mean Randall?
-I guess.

23:14.120 --> 23:16.370
We've been doing these bits
together at parties for a while.

23:16.410 --> 23:18.120
-They're a big hit.
-What, does he think

23:18.160 --> 23:20.000
-he's funny or something?
-He is funny.

23:20.040 --> 23:22.710
-You're kidding. -No.
He's a professional comedian.

23:22.750 --> 23:25.170
He was even thinking we could
get some work doing industrials.

23:25.210 --> 23:27.090
-Industrials?
-Yeah.

23:27.130 --> 23:29.590
What, you're gonna spin around
on a platform hawking Buicks?

23:29.630 --> 23:32.010
What's wrong with that? Buicks
are very fine automobiles.

23:32.050 --> 23:33.720
Miriam,
he just sold you some line

23:33.760 --> 23:35.680
'cause he wants
to get in your pants.

23:35.720 --> 23:37.470
He does not want
to get in my pants.

23:37.520 --> 23:39.850
-He wants to fuck you.
-He wants me to work with him..

23:39.890 --> 23:42.020
He says we'll be like
Nichols and May.

23:42.060 --> 23:43.440
Nichols and May don't fuck.

23:43.480 --> 23:45.110
Nichols and May totally fuck.

23:45.150 --> 23:47.320
-That's not what he says.
-I walked in on them once

23:47.360 --> 23:49.530
in the bathroom here-- even
their fucking was hilarious.

23:49.570 --> 23:51.530
